                "RPPOV": "[ROLEPLAY MODIFIER]\nThe user has requested a change to the default POV. For your next response, please ignore any previous POV formatting and apply the following:\nUSER REFERENCE: Refer to {{user}} using second person (\"you/your\")\nNARRATION STYLE: Write as an external narrator in third person\n- Describe {{char}} actions, thoughts, and feelings in third person (\"Rein smiled,\" \"her heart raced\")\n- Refer to {{user}} in second person (\"you,\" \"your hand,\" \"your eyes\")\n- Example: \"{{char}} took your hand, her heart racing as she squeezed gently.\"",
